{"tid":304651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！一名手持國旗區旗、並戴著紅色帽的學生突然在停機坪身體不適倒地！","createTime":"2017-07-01T05:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T12:58:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":376,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec91313bcdd6ce04352044edec2fb5a01983790a","tid":304651,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【希望小朋友無事】國家主席習近平結束3日訪港行程，將乘坐專機離開香港。在機場停機坪，一批手持國旗區旗、並戴著紅色帽的學生，分別站在地氈兩旁，準備歡送習近平。其中一名小朋友突然身體不適倒地，由職員扶起離開。<br />\n<br />\n(莊振邦攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/19575019_1459801217392294_5196505016241518006_o.jpg?oh=033cfbaef8ed162eff2137e764ea5918&amp;oe=59C419A6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F19575019_1459801217392294_5196505016241518006_o.jpg%3Foh%3D033cfbaef8ed162eff2137e764ea5918%26oe%3D59C419A6&h=6bdcf6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fam730hk%2F&d=y7gdkFo918GblnQd%2F2QIJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b16b4830\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/</a>"},{"pid":"343c81a2e46601cddf34f7f550b30c0f6ec78991","tid":304651,"uid":8681,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"要個肥仔大熱天時暴曬唔中暑就奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b134bf61c591c727615c61ab6a1b1c1bf1cbf167","tid":304651,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im